{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLCanvasElement: contextlost event","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/contextlost_event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","browserCompat":["api.HTMLCanvasElement.contextlost_event"],"baseline":{"baseline":false,"support":{"chrome":"99","chrome_android":"99","edge":"99"}},"sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Instance properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/height\"><code>height</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/mozOpaque\"><code>mozOpaque</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" title=\"Non-standard. Check cross-browser support before using.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Non-standard</span>\n</abbr><abbr class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" title=\"Deprecated. Not for use in new websites.\">\n  <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Deprecated</span>\n</abbr></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/width\"><code>width</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Instance methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/captureStream\"><code>captureStream()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/getContext\"><code>getContext()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/toBlob\"><code>toBlob()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/toDataURL\"><code>toDataURL()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/transferControlToOffscreen\"><code>transferControlToOffscreen()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><em><code>contextlost</code> <abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/contextrestored_event\"><code>contextrestored</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/webglcontextcreationerror_event\"><code>webglcontextcreationerror</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/webglcontextlost_event\"><code>webglcontextlost</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/webglcontextrestored_event\"><code>webglcontextrestored</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","sidebarMacro":"APIRef","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>This is an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Writing_guidelines/Experimental_deprecated_obsolete#experimental\">experimental technology</a></strong><br>Check the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility table</a> carefully before using this in production.</p></div>\n<p>\n  The <strong><code>contextlost</code></strong> event of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas API</a> is fired if the user agent detects that the backing storage associated with a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a> context is lost.\n  Contexts can be lost for several reasons like driver crashes or the application runs out of memory, etc.\n</p>\n<p>\n  By default the user agent will attempt to restore the context and then fire the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/contextrestored_event\"><code>contextrestored</code> event</a>.\n  User code can prevent the context from being restored by calling <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/preventDefault\"><code>Event.preventDefault()</code></a> during event handling.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Use the event name in methods like <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\" title=\"addEventListener()\"><code>addEventListener()</code></a>, or set an event handler property.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">js</span></p><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"contextlost\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function-variable function\">oncontextlost</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"event_type","title":"Event type","isH3":false,"content":"<p>A generic <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The code fragment below detects the <code>contextlost</code> event.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">js</span></p><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> canvas <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"canvas\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\ncanvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"contextlost\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>To prevent the context from being restored the code might instead look like this:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">js</span></p><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> canvas <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"canvas\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\ncanvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"contextlost\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">preventDefault</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-contextlost","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.HTMLCanvasElement.contextlost_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLCanvasElement.contextlost_event"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/contextrestored_event\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement: contextrestored</code> event</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/isContextLost\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D.isContextLost()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Event type","id":"event_type"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The contextlost event of the Canvas API is fired if the user agent detects that the backing storage associated with a CanvasRenderingContext2D context is lost.\n  Contexts can be lost for several reasons like driver crashes or the application runs out of memory, etc.","popularity":0.0006,"modified":"2023-09-22T07:41:39.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/htmlcanvaselement/contextlost_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/api/htmlcanvaselement/contextlost_event/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/8783ce54d738ba294f85fb25d935e7e6e5459a34","filename":"index.md"},"short_title":"contextlost","parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"References"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement","title":"HTMLCanvasElement"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/contextlost_event","title":"contextlost"}],"pageTitle":"HTMLCanvasElement: contextlost event - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}